Mysql for python needs MySQLdb.
to check if it is installed in your system 

put below python code in a file and excute it:

#!/usr/bin/python

import MySQLdb


if error shows follow instructions below and run commands given below
Download tar File MySQL-python-1.2.4b4.tar,extract it

cd MySQL-python-1.2.4b4
python setup.py build
python setup.py install

(may need sudo permission to install)  
